WEBVTT

01:52.160 --> 01:57.590
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.500 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 35]

02:32.000 --> 02:34.460
The Dark Wolves are indeed
incredibly fast.

02:34.940 --> 02:36.290
Let's set off immediately.

02:36.290 --> 02:37.620
There is no time to rest.

02:38.590 --> 02:39.850
Yes, Your Excellency.

02:42.290 --> 02:43.410
Your Excellency?

02:57.130 --> 02:58.730
He is actually the governor.

02:58.730 --> 03:00.130
The whole Nine Cities knows

03:00.130 --> 03:02.520
the relationship between
the governor and Fan Yun.

03:02.520 --> 03:04.480
No wonder they are so close.

03:04.480 --> 03:05.730
It seems that I've...

03:08.480 --> 03:09.540
Fourth Lady Zheng.

03:11.320 --> 03:14.380
There is something
I haven't had time to explain to you.

03:15.170 --> 03:15.930
I

03:16.200 --> 03:17.730
didn't mean to deceive you.

03:18.520 --> 03:20.180
Because of my special status,

03:20.390 --> 03:22.920
I couldn't make a high-profile visit
to Jing City.

03:22.920 --> 03:24.350
I had to take on a different identity.

03:24.350 --> 03:26.210
You don't have to explain it to me.

03:26.700 --> 03:27.950
If I were you,

03:28.010 --> 03:29.470
I would have done the same.

03:30.060 --> 03:32.190
I just should have guessed it earlier.

03:33.640 --> 03:34.640
Your Excellency.

03:36.079 --> 03:37.170
If my granduncle

03:37.170 --> 03:39.700
really did something
he shouldn't have done,

03:40.060 --> 03:41.590
then he should be punished.

03:42.640 --> 03:44.040
However, not everyone in Jing City

03:44.040 --> 03:46.320
wants to stand against the Nine Cities.

03:47.200 --> 03:48.460
I hope Your Excellency

03:49.690 --> 03:51.220
will not harm the innocent.

03:54.079 --> 03:55.730
The election for the clan leader
of the Zheng family

03:55.730 --> 03:56.970
has started early.

03:57.880 --> 03:59.540
Which brother do you support?

04:03.130 --> 04:04.790
My eldest brother, Zheng Jin,

04:04.800 --> 04:06.130
is a reckless man.

04:06.970 --> 04:08.830
And my second brother, Zheng Shi,

04:08.970 --> 04:10.370
is unpredictable.

04:11.250 --> 04:13.050
Even my third brother has become

04:13.080 --> 04:15.340
increasingly scheming in recent years.

04:16.000 --> 04:18.399
No matter who becomes
the next clan leader,

04:18.850 --> 04:20.190
the future of the Zheng family

04:20.190 --> 04:21.310
is uncertain.

04:23.040 --> 04:23.830
Have you

04:24.520 --> 04:26.120
never considered yourself?

04:28.640 --> 04:29.300
Me?

04:29.710 --> 04:30.340
Yes.

04:34.840 --> 04:37.060
My three brothers are fighting fiercely

04:37.060 --> 04:39.030
for the position of the clan leader.

04:39.030 --> 04:41.159
They have long torn away all pretense.

04:41.300 --> 04:42.659
If I get involved too,

04:44.120 --> 04:45.200
the Zheng family

04:45.310 --> 04:46.909
will definitely fall apart.

04:48.280 --> 04:49.560
The significance of the clan leader

04:49.560 --> 04:51.180
is to unite the Zheng family,

04:51.370 --> 04:53.010
gather the strength of the family,

04:53.010 --> 04:54.640
and help the family prosper.

04:55.370 --> 04:56.720
It is not meant to be

04:56.840 --> 04:58.350
a tool for personal gain.

05:04.720 --> 05:05.760
Our Master is determined

05:05.760 --> 05:07.610
to go against the Nine Cities this time.

05:07.610 --> 05:08.610
Our Zheng's Army has already lost

05:08.610 --> 05:10.470
the ceremonial review this time.

05:11.080 --> 05:11.960
At a time like this,

05:11.960 --> 05:13.580
planning a rebellion

05:13.720 --> 05:15.600
is nothing but a death wish.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.320
My mother told me that

05:17.320 --> 05:18.810
if Qi's Army really attacks,

05:18.810 --> 05:20.140
I should run for my life.

05:21.740 --> 05:22.940
Let's keep drinking.

05:48.040 --> 05:50.570
Zheng Tao has made an enemy
of the Nine Cities.

05:50.720 --> 05:52.380
His crimes are unforgivable.

05:52.560 --> 05:54.020
Lay down your weapons now,

05:54.310 --> 05:55.840
and I will spare your lives.

06:06.320 --> 06:08.230
Forgive us, Your Excellency.

06:10.280 --> 06:11.880
You know what's good for you.

06:20.110 --> 06:20.840
Is your wound

06:21.320 --> 06:22.370
going to be okay?

06:23.820 --> 06:24.850
As long as you are here,

06:24.850 --> 06:25.680
I won't die.

06:30.340 --> 06:32.610
Tomorrow is the day
of the clan leader election.

06:32.610 --> 06:33.570
Could I ask you

06:33.630 --> 06:35.290
to comb my hair in the morning?

06:36.080 --> 06:37.610
Why ask me to comb your hair?

06:38.500 --> 06:40.560
You clearly have servants and maids.

06:40.690 --> 06:42.090
On such an important day,

06:42.320 --> 06:43.370
I want to ask someone important to me

06:43.370 --> 06:44.380
to comb my hair

06:44.690 --> 06:45.720
for good luck.

06:49.130 --> 06:50.730
I don't know how to comb hair.

06:52.720 --> 06:54.080
But if you are willing,

06:55.090 --> 06:56.550
I can take you to the scene.

07:00.840 --> 07:02.370
I'm sure you want to be there

07:02.620 --> 07:04.420
to gather information and so on.

07:04.810 --> 07:06.720
After all, the Zheng family's
clan leader election

07:06.720 --> 07:09.780
will directly affect
the stability of the Nine Cities.

07:14.810 --> 07:15.570
But...

07:16.090 --> 07:18.400
I've never combed
anyone else's hair before.

07:18.400 --> 07:19.490
If it looks ugly,

07:19.570 --> 07:20.570
don't blame me.

07:22.640 --> 07:23.770
I look forward to it.

07:40.200 --> 07:41.730
Do you hope I'll be elected?

07:43.760 --> 07:46.090
Can you guarantee
the stability of the Nine Cities?

07:46.090 --> 07:48.950
I don't care about
the stability of the Nine Cities.

07:56.610 --> 07:57.610
I'm done combing.

08:02.250 --> 08:03.080
Are you okay?

08:05.480 --> 08:07.280
It seems you still care about me.

08:08.080 --> 08:09.080
I just wonder when

08:09.450 --> 08:12.050
I will be able to drink
the tea brewed by your own hands,

08:12.050 --> 08:12.570
Fan Yun.

08:20.250 --> 08:21.570
I've combed your hair.

08:22.400 --> 08:23.640
When can we leave?

08:24.080 --> 08:26.080
Turning hostile before
even achieving your goal?

08:26.080 --> 08:27.530
I'm not turning hostile.

08:28.260 --> 08:30.190
You're the one who keeps stalling.

08:30.370 --> 08:31.080
What,

08:31.890 --> 08:33.490
are you worried I'd run away,

08:33.610 --> 08:34.630
or did you never

08:34.970 --> 08:36.970
intend to take me in the first place?

08:39.799 --> 08:41.890
Prepare another set of servant's clothes.

08:41.890 --> 08:42.610
Yes, sir.

08:49.110 --> 08:51.490
[Magnificent and awe-inspiring]

08:54.760 --> 08:57.160
Originally, Zheng Jin, Zheng Shi,
and Zheng Xian

08:57.160 --> 08:59.730
were competing for
the position of clan leader.

08:59.730 --> 09:00.970
But Zheng Shi

09:02.490 --> 09:03.970
was utterly rebellious

09:03.970 --> 09:05.680
and disregarded human ethics.

09:05.680 --> 09:07.800
He murdered his older brother,

09:09.490 --> 09:10.380
Zheng Jin.

09:11.560 --> 09:13.250
This is too cruel.

09:22.450 --> 09:24.210
Young Master Shi killed
Eldest Young Master?

09:24.210 --> 09:26.610
How could Young Master Shi be so vicious?

09:26.610 --> 09:28.250
I received the news

09:28.250 --> 09:29.800
that Jin was murdered,

09:29.800 --> 09:32.000
and immediately rushed back
to Jing City from Ling'an.

09:32.000 --> 09:33.250
Poor me,

09:34.090 --> 09:37.010
I didn't even get to see him
one last time.

09:37.970 --> 09:39.370
In that case,

09:40.560 --> 09:42.090
the position of clan leader

09:43.600 --> 09:45.620
will be inherited by Xian.

09:46.780 --> 09:48.380
I hope all the relatives here

09:48.400 --> 09:50.420
will assist Xian well in the future

09:51.010 --> 09:53.640
and revive the prestige
of the Zheng family.

09:53.640 --> 09:54.730
But,

09:54.730 --> 09:56.590
does he have the clan leader ring?

09:57.250 --> 09:58.130
If he does,

09:58.170 --> 09:59.560
we will naturally acknowledge him

09:59.560 --> 10:01.440
as the new clan leader
of our Zheng family.

10:01.440 --> 10:02.920
That's right.

10:02.920 --> 10:03.880
Of course.

10:04.160 --> 10:07.330
Our Zheng family
has always revered the clan leader ring.

10:07.330 --> 10:08.850
Only the one who holds the ring

10:08.850 --> 10:11.450
can become
the clan leader of our Zheng family.

10:12.330 --> 10:13.080
Today,

10:19.250 --> 10:20.800
I will bestow this ring

10:21.440 --> 10:23.090
upon Xian,

10:24.610 --> 10:25.520
to help him

10:26.120 --> 10:28.320
take on the position of the clan leader.

10:37.850 --> 10:39.310
Why are you in such a hurry?

10:51.310 --> 10:52.770
Why didn't you wait for me?

10:55.920 --> 10:57.720
You are already the clan leader.

11:09.760 --> 11:12.080
You still have the nerve
to attend the election?

11:12.080 --> 11:13.290
Why wouldn't I?

11:15.280 --> 11:16.680
You say I killed Jin.

11:17.280 --> 11:18.740
But where is the evidence?

11:19.610 --> 11:20.440
Evidence?

11:21.250 --> 11:23.050
You are audacious and reckless.

11:23.310 --> 11:24.370
Have you forgotten

11:24.490 --> 11:27.890
that there were others around
when you committed the murder?

11:38.280 --> 11:39.210
Don't be afraid.

11:39.400 --> 11:40.560
I was wrong that day.

11:40.870 --> 11:42.670
I shouldn't have hit you so hard.

11:43.370 --> 11:45.370
Let me see how your wound is healing.

11:48.850 --> 11:49.850
You can't show it?

11:51.090 --> 11:52.820
That means you are not injured.

11:53.640 --> 11:55.370
If Zheng Xian isn't injured,

11:55.640 --> 11:57.330
then he was lying just now.

11:59.010 --> 12:00.440
The claim that I killed Jin

12:00.440 --> 12:01.900
is completely unfounded.

12:02.560 --> 12:04.330
But if you, Zheng Xian, killed him

12:04.330 --> 12:05.380
and framed me,

12:05.760 --> 12:07.960
it'd be a good move
to reap the benefits.

12:08.090 --> 12:09.440
Nonsense!

12:10.970 --> 12:13.100
The clan leader ring is in my hands now.

12:13.440 --> 12:15.640
I am the clan leader of the Zheng family.

12:15.960 --> 12:18.220
How dare you disrespect the clan leader?

12:18.330 --> 12:20.410
Aren't you afraid that,
with a single order,

12:20.410 --> 12:22.330
I'll have you punished
according to the clan rules?

12:22.330 --> 12:25.370
The clan leader ring
has always been kept by the clan leader.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.010
The previous clan leader
of the Zheng family

12:27.010 --> 12:28.370
lived in Ling'an for a long time.

12:28.370 --> 12:30.160
You guys probably
haven't seen much of him,

12:30.160 --> 12:32.290
let alone know the secret of this ring.

12:32.520 --> 12:33.440
Secret?

12:34.330 --> 12:35.370
What secret?

12:35.370 --> 12:37.730
Today, in front of all the relatives,

12:38.330 --> 12:40.390
I will reveal the secret of this ring.

12:40.850 --> 12:41.610
Hand it over.

12:49.970 --> 12:51.850
The gemstone on the clan leader ring

12:51.850 --> 12:53.120
is polished from a very rare

12:53.120 --> 12:54.520
bloodstone in the world.

12:54.970 --> 12:56.850
Not only is its color red like blood,

12:56.850 --> 12:58.160
but if you press it hard enough,

12:58.160 --> 13:00.370
it will also ooze a blood-like liquid.

13:02.850 --> 13:03.760
Actually,

13:04.280 --> 13:05.410
the clan leader ring

13:05.850 --> 13:07.850
is also the token of the clan leader.

13:09.800 --> 13:12.200
That is indeed true about this ring.

13:13.500 --> 13:14.160
Zheng Xian.

13:15.400 --> 13:18.290
You actually tried to get away
with a fake ring.

13:19.160 --> 13:20.040
How

13:20.040 --> 13:21.920
disheartening.

13:22.760 --> 13:25.920
Where is the real ring now?

13:27.730 --> 13:28.800
In my opinion,

13:28.800 --> 13:30.330
having the ring or not

13:30.330 --> 13:33.440
isn't the only criterion
for determining the clan leader.

13:33.440 --> 13:36.100
It also depends on
his character and abilities.

13:37.850 --> 13:39.130
That being said,

13:39.130 --> 13:40.250
in any case,

13:40.250 --> 13:42.010
Zheng Xian's actions

13:42.010 --> 13:42.730
show that

13:42.730 --> 13:44.400
he himself doesn't believe

13:44.400 --> 13:46.760
he can lead the Zheng family
to resurgence.

13:46.760 --> 13:47.680
If you ask me,

13:48.040 --> 13:49.520
Young Master Shi

13:49.520 --> 13:51.850
is definitely going to be the clan leader.

13:52.280 --> 13:53.730
That's right.

13:53.730 --> 13:55.730
We all choose Young Master Shi.

13:55.730 --> 13:56.490
Enough!

14:01.760 --> 14:03.010
Today's election

14:04.610 --> 14:05.890
has become a farce.

14:09.090 --> 14:10.280
Xian.

14:11.210 --> 14:12.010
Grandfather.

14:14.730 --> 14:16.390
Stop embarrassing yourself.

14:16.730 --> 14:17.560
Let's go.

14:35.970 --> 14:38.300
I appreciate your support, my relatives.

14:38.520 --> 14:39.630
From now on,

14:39.920 --> 14:41.760
I will inherit Grandfather's dying wish

14:41.760 --> 14:44.020
and lead the Zheng family towards glory.

14:44.520 --> 14:45.380
In 3 days,

14:45.520 --> 14:48.780
please come to attend
my clan leader succession ceremony.

14:48.970 --> 14:50.310
Alright.

15:35.160 --> 15:36.290
If there's a chance,

15:37.920 --> 15:39.380
could we meet in my dreams?

15:44.680 --> 15:46.480
I really miss you, Grandfather.

16:00.010 --> 16:01.040
This map is...

16:01.890 --> 16:04.440
The defense map of Jing City
drawn for me by Juyun Pavilion.

16:04.440 --> 16:05.470
With this map,

16:05.800 --> 16:07.760
the military defense of Jing City
is clear at a glance.

16:07.760 --> 16:10.360
Zheng Tao won't be able to play
any more tricks.

16:20.330 --> 16:22.060
So you were prepared all along.

16:22.490 --> 16:24.490
But you just became the clan leader.

16:24.680 --> 16:26.680
Are you really going to go against
the whole Zheng family?

16:26.680 --> 16:27.490
I am doing this

16:27.490 --> 16:29.090
to protect the Zheng family.

16:29.520 --> 16:31.280
The one trying to bring disgrace
upon the Zheng family

16:31.280 --> 16:32.250
is Zheng Tao.

16:32.610 --> 16:33.850
If he really rebels,

16:34.970 --> 16:36.130
the whole Zheng family

16:36.130 --> 16:38.760
will become the common enemy
of the Nine Cities.

16:38.760 --> 16:40.370
By then, with internal
and external troubles,

16:40.370 --> 16:42.300
the Zheng family will be wiped out.

16:42.370 --> 16:43.890
Grandfather's spirit in heaven

16:43.890 --> 16:45.970
won't be able to rest in peace that way.

16:45.970 --> 16:47.010
Then why don't you

16:47.400 --> 16:49.060
join hands with the governor?

16:49.210 --> 16:51.340
If the governor really gets involved,

16:51.440 --> 16:53.560
the Zheng family's rebellion
will be confirmed.

16:53.560 --> 16:56.010
By then, everyone in the Zheng family
will bear the crime.

16:56.010 --> 16:57.760
If I can nip this in the bud

16:57.760 --> 16:59.000
before it happens,

16:59.130 --> 17:00.650
the Zheng family can stand tall

17:00.650 --> 17:03.050
and continue to survive
in the Nine Cities.

17:03.610 --> 17:04.680
But I believe

17:05.440 --> 17:07.770
the governor can handle this matter well.

17:08.440 --> 17:09.520
I don't think so.

17:10.000 --> 17:12.160
The Zheng family has kept to itself
for many years.

17:12.160 --> 17:14.020
Qi Zheng is just showing his edge.

17:14.240 --> 17:16.609
Whether it's incorporation or recapture,

17:16.609 --> 17:19.210
the hardest thing to win over
is people's hearts.

17:19.210 --> 17:20.069
Let him be.

17:21.480 --> 17:22.530
I only care that

17:23.329 --> 17:25.859
you probably
wouldn't want to marry a sinner.

17:26.530 --> 17:28.130
You mean,

17:29.440 --> 17:30.290
marry you?

17:30.850 --> 17:31.480
Yeah.

17:32.200 --> 17:33.850
Aren't we already engaged?

17:35.160 --> 17:37.020
We should hold the ceremony soon.

17:38.530 --> 17:39.920
At a time like this,

17:40.570 --> 17:42.610
you still have the mood to joke around?

17:42.610 --> 17:43.370
Lady Fan Yun.

17:43.610 --> 17:44.610
Lady Fan Yun.

17:46.240 --> 17:47.200
Zheng Xi, you're back.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.090
Lady Fan Yun.

17:49.640 --> 17:50.570
Shi...

17:51.200 --> 17:51.850
Zheng Xi.

17:52.330 --> 17:54.440
Where have you been these past two days?

17:54.440 --> 17:55.240
I...

17:55.680 --> 17:56.480
Zheng Xi,

17:56.480 --> 17:57.170
how is it?

17:57.450 --> 17:59.640
Did everything go smoothly on your end?

17:59.640 --> 18:00.570
Second Brother,

18:01.100 --> 18:04.290
I want to talk to Second Sister-in-Law
alone.

18:06.720 --> 18:07.330
Okay.

18:13.680 --> 18:15.080
When Liu Mu reported to me

18:15.370 --> 18:16.640
that you had already led Qi's Army

18:16.640 --> 18:17.950
to Jing City,

18:18.450 --> 18:19.560
I was very pleased.

18:19.810 --> 18:21.170
Your march this time

18:21.370 --> 18:22.530
can be considered lightning fast.

18:22.530 --> 18:24.580
Yan Jiang, you didn't get lost
leading the troops?

18:24.580 --> 18:26.850
It seems you really are
suited to be a military general.

18:26.850 --> 18:27.610
Why don't you

18:27.920 --> 18:29.290
give up the pen for the sword

18:29.290 --> 18:30.400
and be my deputy?

18:30.890 --> 18:31.960
Why should I?

18:33.010 --> 18:33.610
By the way,

18:34.460 --> 18:35.280
how is Gao Ran

18:35.420 --> 18:37.280
handling the political affairs?

18:37.960 --> 18:39.810
Gao Ran is extremely diligent

18:39.810 --> 18:40.680
and hardworking.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.680
Every day, he reviews memorials
until late at night.

18:42.680 --> 18:43.400
Moreover,

18:43.490 --> 18:44.800
everything inside and outside
the Qi Residence

18:44.800 --> 18:46.400
has been taken care of by him.

18:46.920 --> 18:48.130
Are you implying that

18:48.180 --> 18:49.200
when I was handling
the government affairs,

18:49.200 --> 18:51.260
I was not diligent and hard-working?

18:51.610 --> 18:53.320
No, I didn't mean that.

18:53.580 --> 18:55.290
Your Excellency, you're naturally

18:55.290 --> 18:56.290
wise and brilliant,

18:56.290 --> 18:57.430
shining like the sun and the moon.

18:57.430 --> 18:58.240
Then tell me,

18:58.770 --> 18:59.890
compared with Gao Ran,

18:59.890 --> 19:00.690
who is better?

19:02.440 --> 19:04.700
I don't know the answer to this question.

19:08.160 --> 19:09.680
Gao Ran is too boring.

19:09.680 --> 19:11.370
He just stays in the residence every day.

19:11.370 --> 19:13.250
When you were home,
the residence was much livelier.

19:13.250 --> 19:14.050
So,

19:14.570 --> 19:16.430
you're better, Your Excellency.

19:17.770 --> 19:19.370
You know what's good for you.

19:19.370 --> 19:21.770
Although it didn't sound like
a compliment to me.

19:21.770 --> 19:22.700
You've grown up.

19:25.640 --> 19:27.940
About Gao Ran and me switching identities,

19:27.940 --> 19:29.470
has any minister found out?

19:32.290 --> 19:34.330
The officials in the city have not.

19:34.770 --> 19:36.370
but...

19:38.680 --> 19:39.570
But what?

19:41.240 --> 19:42.400
Hurry up and say it.

19:42.400 --> 19:45.130
But after you left Ling'an,

19:45.130 --> 19:47.270
Wei Shisan stayed
in the residence all day,

19:47.270 --> 19:49.560
so she somewhat noticed some clues.

19:49.920 --> 19:51.090
Shisan knows?

19:52.240 --> 19:53.500
Then the two of them...

19:55.720 --> 19:57.720
-As you expected.
-As you expected.

20:06.720 --> 20:07.720
Your Excellency.

20:07.720 --> 20:09.720
I heard that Zheng Tao's arsenal

20:09.720 --> 20:11.580
was completely destroyed by you.

20:11.850 --> 20:14.680
He won't be able to cause
much of a stir, then.

20:15.050 --> 20:16.090
Why don't we take advantage of tonight

20:16.090 --> 20:17.890
and attack Jing City directly?

20:17.890 --> 20:18.580
Yeah.

20:18.920 --> 20:20.770
Right after I praised you both?

20:20.770 --> 20:21.570
Of course not.

20:22.090 --> 20:23.810
We must not rush this matter.

20:25.240 --> 20:26.770
If we enter the city rashly,

20:27.920 --> 20:29.960
it will definitely enrage Zheng Tao.

20:29.960 --> 20:32.100
This matter requires careful planning.

20:32.100 --> 20:34.000
But what other way is there
if we don't attack by force?

20:34.000 --> 20:34.810
Besides,

20:35.050 --> 20:37.050
Your Excellency,
aren't you worried about Fan Yun?

20:37.050 --> 20:37.720
Yeah.

20:39.520 --> 20:41.120
If we attack the city rashly,

20:41.570 --> 20:43.770
innocent civilians
will definitely be hurt.

20:43.770 --> 20:44.830
I won't agree to it.

20:48.160 --> 20:49.220
I also believe that

20:50.130 --> 20:51.460
Fan Yun understands me.

20:56.440 --> 20:57.400
So,

20:58.200 --> 20:59.660
you know everything about

20:59.850 --> 21:00.980
Gao Ran's identity?

21:03.850 --> 21:05.640
The governor is worried about your safety,

21:05.640 --> 21:08.300
so he asked me to come back
and check on you first.

21:08.770 --> 21:09.760
Lady Fan Yun,

21:09.960 --> 21:11.400
I envy you.

21:11.720 --> 21:14.530
If a man in this world

21:14.610 --> 21:17.210
would treat me the way
the governor treats you,

21:17.420 --> 21:19.220
I would be so perfectly content.

21:22.090 --> 21:24.420
The governor asks you to endure
a little longer.

21:24.420 --> 21:25.280
When he returns,

21:25.280 --> 21:26.930
he will definitely save you first.

21:26.930 --> 21:28.260
Saving me is secondary.

21:29.290 --> 21:30.820
Right now, I'm worried that

21:31.200 --> 21:32.610
if Zheng Tao

21:32.610 --> 21:34.230
really fights Qi's Army,

21:34.850 --> 21:36.200
the people of Jing City

21:36.200 --> 21:37.600
will inevitably suffer.

21:37.970 --> 21:40.070
The devastation in the city

21:40.680 --> 21:43.080
is absolutely not
what anyone wants to see.

21:43.330 --> 21:45.510
That is a scene no one wants to see.

21:46.200 --> 21:48.050
But now, Jing City and Qi's Army

21:48.050 --> 21:48.920
are at odds,

21:48.920 --> 21:50.610
and the army is bearing down
on the border.

21:50.610 --> 21:52.610
No matter which side strikes first,

21:53.000 --> 21:54.050
Jing City

21:54.050 --> 21:56.090
will inevitably witness bloodshed.

21:56.090 --> 21:56.870
Yes.

21:57.370 --> 21:58.230
These two sides

21:58.400 --> 21:59.860
absolutely cannot fight.

22:00.090 --> 22:01.570
Do you have any good ideas?

22:02.640 --> 22:03.960
An idea...

22:04.960 --> 22:07.160
Actually, we could use the deployment map

22:07.160 --> 22:08.760
to sneak into Jing City first

22:08.890 --> 22:10.640
and control their military camp.

22:10.640 --> 22:11.480
This way,

22:11.480 --> 22:12.890
they would lose their support.

22:12.890 --> 22:14.350
If we then attack the city,

22:14.640 --> 22:16.480
we can minimize casualties.

22:19.050 --> 22:19.680
Zheng Xi,

22:20.200 --> 22:21.810
I need you to leave the city now

22:21.810 --> 22:22.940
to tell the governor

22:23.130 --> 22:25.000
that he absolutely must not
force an attack on the city.

22:25.000 --> 22:25.610
Okay.

22:25.920 --> 22:27.120
I'll go immediately.

22:27.520 --> 22:28.410
Wait.

22:55.240 --> 22:56.610
Fan Yun drew this?

22:58.200 --> 22:59.090
Yes.

22:59.720 --> 23:01.810
It was as if it were imprinted
in her mind.

23:01.810 --> 23:03.160
She drew it swiftly

23:03.160 --> 23:04.560
and without hesitation.

23:05.850 --> 23:08.380
Lady Fan Yun is truly
an extraordinary woman.

23:08.660 --> 23:10.850
Your Excellency, you're most fortunate

23:10.850 --> 23:12.780
to have Lady Fan Yun's assistance.

23:13.640 --> 23:16.610
Lady Fan Yun also asked me to pass
a message to you.

23:17.890 --> 23:18.640
Go on.

23:19.790 --> 23:20.620
Lady Fan Yun said

23:20.620 --> 23:23.480
you absolutely must not
force an attack on the city.

23:33.570 --> 23:34.890
Our minds think alike.

23:35.810 --> 23:37.270
The one who understands me

23:38.680 --> 23:39.370
is her.

23:49.280 --> 23:51.280
It seems that we are not the only ones

23:51.290 --> 23:52.720
waiting to strike on the eve

23:52.720 --> 23:54.320
of the clan leader ceremony.

23:58.770 --> 23:59.770
Your Excellency.

24:02.610 --> 24:04.130
You are?

24:05.480 --> 24:07.130
No need for disguises anymore.

24:07.130 --> 24:08.130
I, Liu Mu,

24:08.130 --> 24:10.260
am going to fight my way back this time.

24:10.640 --> 24:12.440
Wei Ying, Yan Jiang.

24:13.530 --> 24:14.570
-Yes, Your Excellency.
-Yes, Your Excellency.

24:14.570 --> 24:17.200
We will lead the elite troops
to sneak in overnight.

24:17.200 --> 24:19.770
The Zheng family's internal conflict
will surely hurt both sides.

24:19.770 --> 24:21.630
We'll take them by surprise then.

24:22.680 --> 24:23.340
-Yes.
-Yes.

24:25.330 --> 24:27.050
Your Excellency.

24:27.610 --> 24:28.410
What about me?

24:29.480 --> 24:30.240
You?

24:31.850 --> 24:33.980
You will be the main general tomorrow.

24:34.240 --> 24:35.050
Great.

24:35.770 --> 24:37.700
Let these opportunistic ingrates

24:37.810 --> 24:39.340
remember me, Gate Cdr. Liu.

25:36.810 --> 25:38.870
They've increased the guards again.

25:39.680 --> 25:41.050
How can I get away,

25:41.050 --> 25:42.640
sneak into the clan leader's hall,

25:42.640 --> 25:44.330
gather news on Zheng's Army,

25:44.680 --> 25:45.770
and pass the info

25:45.770 --> 25:46.770
to Qi Zheng?

26:01.770 --> 26:03.300
Second Young Master Zheng.

26:06.840 --> 26:10.440
You're accompanying me to the
clan leader's ceremony tomorrow.

26:10.540 --> 26:11.460
Don't drink too much tonight.

26:11.460 --> 26:13.060
The clan leader's ceremony?

26:13.640 --> 26:15.160
You want me to go with you?

26:17.160 --> 26:19.690
I didn't fight for
the clan leader's position

26:20.000 --> 26:21.290
to seize the so-called

26:21.290 --> 26:22.850
overwhelming power.

26:24.810 --> 26:26.090
The things they give everything

26:26.090 --> 26:27.240
to fight for

26:27.430 --> 26:28.840
mean nothing to me.

26:31.770 --> 26:33.200
There are only 2 things in this world

26:33.200 --> 26:34.860
that are most important to me.

26:38.370 --> 26:39.770
Do you know what they are?

26:44.000 --> 26:45.200
Grandfather and you.

26:50.240 --> 26:51.300
So rest assured.

26:52.960 --> 26:54.490
Since I'm taking you there,

26:54.890 --> 26:57.220
I'll naturally make proper arrangements

26:57.370 --> 26:58.840
and keep you safe.

27:00.810 --> 27:02.480
Tomorrow, in front of everyone,

27:02.480 --> 27:04.140
I will give you a new identity.

27:08.890 --> 27:09.720
My Lady.

27:10.570 --> 27:11.720
From now on,

27:12.370 --> 27:13.370
no one can ever

27:13.370 --> 27:14.890
lay a finger on you.

27:14.890 --> 27:15.850
"My Lady"?

27:21.160 --> 27:22.690
Second Young Master Zheng,

27:22.890 --> 27:24.890
you might have drunk too much today.

27:26.330 --> 27:28.400
Even if you plan to announce my identity,

27:28.400 --> 27:30.290
it should be as Gate Cdr. Fan.

27:31.200 --> 27:32.130
Our marriage

27:33.440 --> 27:36.040
was just a stalling tactic
to get into the city.

27:36.160 --> 27:37.160
I'll say it again.

27:37.400 --> 27:39.000
Don't take it too seriously.

27:39.570 --> 27:41.770
What if I insist on taking it seriously?

27:54.720 --> 27:56.050
I just hope

27:57.960 --> 27:59.810
you can stay by my side.

28:07.050 --> 28:08.380
Stop talking nonsense.

28:08.960 --> 28:10.240
I'll pour you a cup of tea

28:10.240 --> 28:11.400
to sober you up.

28:15.810 --> 28:17.610
If you really want to pour me tea,

28:18.850 --> 28:20.720
then pour me a cup of sweet dew tea.

28:25.370 --> 28:27.160
According to Jing City's customs,

28:27.160 --> 28:27.920
a woman

28:28.680 --> 28:31.210
only brews sweet dew tea
for the man she loves.

28:32.000 --> 28:33.480
Second Young Master Zheng,

28:33.480 --> 28:34.740
you know very well that

28:36.440 --> 28:37.770
My heart is not with you.

28:44.960 --> 28:46.430
♪ I could have ♪

28:46.460 --> 28:48.060
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

28:48.080 --> 28:51.440
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

28:51.620 --> 28:53.270
♪ Never caging my love ♪

28:53.300 --> 28:57.520
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

28:57.650 --> 29:01.730
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

29:01.990 --> 29:05.300
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

29:04.850 --> 29:05.250
You...

29:05.480 --> 29:11.400
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

29:11.480 --> 29:14.190
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

29:14.210 --> 29:18.170
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

29:18.290 --> 29:20.770
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

29:20.800 --> 29:25.160
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

29:25.180 --> 29:27.810
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

29:27.840 --> 29:32.690
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

29:29.400 --> 29:30.530
Tomorrow...

29:32.710 --> 29:38.940
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

29:34.060 --> 29:35.590
I will attend the ceremony.

29:36.330 --> 29:37.930
But I won't become your lady.

29:40.040 --> 29:49.670
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

29:40.400 --> 29:42.660
I am only the Gate Commander of Jing City.

30:26.330 --> 30:27.300
Master arrives!

30:27.960 --> 30:30.220
The Gate Commander of Jing City arrives!

30:40.440 --> 30:42.100
The auspicious time has come.

30:42.240 --> 30:43.640
All things begin.

30:44.320 --> 30:48.320
Master's ancestor worship ceremony
officially begins.

31:56.330 --> 31:57.860
Second Young Master Zheng!

32:25.850 --> 32:27.310
The ceremony is complete.

32:36.530 --> 32:39.330
You're still a bad seed
who can't change your ways.

32:42.050 --> 32:44.510
Granduncle, are you really that surprised?

32:45.610 --> 32:46.610
Did you really think

32:46.610 --> 32:48.610
I would just sit here and wait to die?

32:48.720 --> 32:50.560
When it comes to the real fight,

32:51.370 --> 32:53.890
you still rely on these wandering rogues.

33:06.260 --> 33:07.790
Second Young Master Zheng.

33:12.640 --> 33:14.720
Zheng Shi colluded with bandits

33:14.720 --> 33:17.200
and betrayed his ancestors.
His crimes are unpardonable.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.570
Execute him on the spot.

33:18.570 --> 33:20.720
Yes. Kill!

34:08.080 --> 34:09.000
Ready!

34:09.370 --> 34:10.080
Load.

34:20.400 --> 34:21.330
Fire!

34:40.150 --> 34:40.820
Let's go.

34:46.920 --> 34:47.719
Grandfather!

34:48.219 --> 34:49.659
I told you before.

34:49.810 --> 34:50.810
I can do this.

34:51.520 --> 34:53.770
The position of clan leader
is definitely mine.

34:53.770 --> 34:54.850
This first shot

34:54.889 --> 34:55.920
is just a warning.

34:57.800 --> 34:59.120
Do you want

34:59.210 --> 35:00.920
all of us to die with you?

35:00.920 --> 35:02.180
What are you afraid of?

35:02.210 --> 35:03.540
You are my grandfather.

35:03.850 --> 35:05.650
Of course I will spare your life.

35:09.890 --> 35:10.730
Shi.

35:11.440 --> 35:13.050
Surrender now.

35:13.480 --> 35:15.600
Hand over the position of clan leader,

35:15.600 --> 35:17.600
and I will leave your corpse intact.

35:17.770 --> 35:19.210
You secretly hoarded gunpowder.

35:19.210 --> 35:20.730
Do you want our Zheng family

35:20.730 --> 35:22.080
to be wiped out?

35:23.140 --> 35:25.650
Since you can hide an arsenal
outside the city,

35:25.650 --> 35:26.960
why can't I?

35:27.600 --> 35:29.730
A Zheng family where
I cannot be the Master

35:29.730 --> 35:31.120
has no reason to exist.

35:31.770 --> 35:32.640
Uncles,

35:35.330 --> 35:37.130
will you accept me as the Master?

35:50.080 --> 35:50.770
Good.

36:08.600 --> 36:10.260
Third Young Master, bad news!

36:10.650 --> 36:12.650
-What happened?
-We were ambushed.

36:22.290 --> 36:23.490
How is that possible?

36:35.770 --> 36:38.440
His Excellency has arrived!

37:00.730 --> 37:02.770
Fan Yun, Gate Commander of Jing City,

37:02.770 --> 37:04.770
shows my respect, Your Excellency.

37:10.250 --> 37:12.250
Greetings, Your Excellency.

37:26.480 --> 37:27.730
You may rise.

37:27.730 --> 37:31.060
-Thank you, Your Excellency.
-Thank you, Your Excellency.

37:37.690 --> 37:39.120
Your Excellency, please forgive

37:39.120 --> 37:40.290
the Zheng family for

37:40.290 --> 37:42.340
failing to welcome you properly.

37:42.560 --> 37:44.840
But may I ask why

37:45.290 --> 37:48.960
you have come to attend
our clan leader election?

37:49.330 --> 37:50.480
Do you think

37:51.400 --> 37:52.890
I'm not qualified to attend

37:52.890 --> 37:54.560
the clan leader election?

38:02.960 --> 38:04.250
The clan leader ring?

38:06.690 --> 38:08.210
Why is it with you?

38:11.080 --> 38:11.770
Everyone,

38:12.440 --> 38:13.440
there is more

38:13.600 --> 38:14.930
to Elder Zheng's death.

38:16.690 --> 38:18.350
Elder Zheng was far-sighted.

38:19.040 --> 38:20.840
He knew the Zheng family's chaos

38:20.920 --> 38:23.180
would threaten the safety of Nine Cities

38:23.480 --> 38:25.280
and implicate innocent people.

38:26.330 --> 38:27.040
So,

38:27.560 --> 38:29.760
he sacrificed his life to save Jing City

38:30.080 --> 38:32.350
and gave this clan leader ring to me.

38:32.890 --> 38:34.290
He hoped I would maintain

38:34.690 --> 38:36.090
the peace of Nine Cities.

38:37.000 --> 38:38.530
But now you have gone astray

38:39.290 --> 38:41.220
and embarked on a path of no return.

38:42.000 --> 38:43.040
Isn't this wasting

38:43.040 --> 38:45.100
Elder Zheng's painstaking efforts?

38:46.120 --> 38:48.520
Yes. He's right.

38:59.920 --> 39:00.810
Your Excellency.

39:00.810 --> 39:02.850
The Zheng family is rebelling.

39:02.850 --> 39:04.600
They hid a batch of gunpowder
outside the city.

39:04.600 --> 39:05.890
They hate me for supporting you

39:05.890 --> 39:07.480
and are forcing me to rebel.

39:07.480 --> 39:09.080
None of this is my wish.

39:09.770 --> 39:12.170
Please reveal the truth, Your Excellency.

39:18.850 --> 39:19.770
Zheng Xian.

39:20.920 --> 39:22.920
Although I am the governor
of the Nine Cities,

39:22.920 --> 39:24.690
I am just a mortal.

39:25.770 --> 39:27.000
I cannot always see through

39:27.000 --> 39:28.730
conspiracies and deceptions.

39:29.890 --> 39:32.350
Occasionally, I make mistakes in judgment.

39:33.370 --> 39:34.370
As for these nice words,

39:34.370 --> 39:36.030
you can say as much as you like.

39:36.170 --> 39:38.600
It is up to me to decide
whether to believe them.

39:38.600 --> 39:39.480
Your Excellency,

39:39.480 --> 39:40.600
you have to believe me.

39:40.600 --> 39:42.250
You must believe me.

39:42.250 --> 39:42.960
Hurry,

39:42.960 --> 39:44.020
give the order now.

39:44.370 --> 39:46.960
I will help you kill these
rebellious traitors.

39:46.960 --> 39:49.040
Even now, you are still obstinate.

39:50.250 --> 39:52.400
Since I could get the gunpowder
outside the city,

39:52.400 --> 39:53.930
I naturally know who did it.

39:59.330 --> 40:00.810
I originally thought that

40:00.810 --> 40:02.850
after the matter in Jing City was over,

40:02.850 --> 40:04.510
I would hold you accountable.

40:05.400 --> 40:07.600
But I didn't expect you to be
even more ruthless than Zheng Tao

40:07.600 --> 40:09.730
and disregard the lives of the people.

40:10.520 --> 40:12.450
Aren't you afraid of retribution?

40:12.810 --> 40:13.610
Retribution?

40:19.210 --> 40:20.120
Let me tell you.

40:21.120 --> 40:22.890
I've come this far in life,

40:23.560 --> 40:25.330
fearing only mediocrity

40:25.520 --> 40:26.440
and being trampled on

40:26.440 --> 40:29.080
like dirt by others!

40:34.120 --> 40:34.810
Guards.

40:35.600 --> 40:37.890
Strip Zheng Xian of his official uniform,

40:37.890 --> 40:39.150
throw him into prison,

40:39.650 --> 40:41.170
and interrogate him strictly.

40:41.170 --> 40:41.850
Yes.

40:44.120 --> 40:44.730
Get lost!

40:47.000 --> 40:48.600
Watch out, Your Excellency!

40:49.960 --> 40:50.560
Come on!

40:51.730 --> 40:52.520
Come on!

40:53.290 --> 40:54.250
You people

40:54.600 --> 40:56.690
who stand above others every day.

40:57.280 --> 40:58.680
I was only one step away

40:59.210 --> 41:01.650
from killing all of you.

41:04.960 --> 41:06.600
And you, Zheng Tao!

41:07.210 --> 41:08.060
Xian...

41:08.290 --> 41:11.220
Do you know who killed
your beloved eldest grandson?

41:14.000 --> 41:14.850
It was me.

41:19.690 --> 41:20.850
Since childhood,

41:21.770 --> 41:23.500
you were loved by Grandfather.

41:23.730 --> 41:25.960
Second Brother was loved by Granduncle.

41:25.960 --> 41:27.690
None of you ever cared about me.

41:28.960 --> 41:30.960
Now I will show you

41:30.960 --> 41:31.960
how I, Zheng Xian,

41:32.480 --> 41:34.370
will trample you all under my feet

41:34.370 --> 41:36.210
one step at a time.

41:38.120 --> 41:39.850
He was your eldest brother.

41:39.850 --> 41:41.370
So what if he was?

41:42.250 --> 41:44.730
You never truly saw me anyway.

41:44.730 --> 41:46.320
-You've gone crazy!
-I am crazy!

41:46.320 --> 41:47.550
I am crazy!

41:48.810 --> 41:50.610
I am completely crazy this time.

41:51.090 --> 41:52.400
It's because I'm crazy

41:53.080 --> 41:54.210
that you finally looked me

41:54.210 --> 41:55.950
in the eye today.

41:57.600 --> 41:59.770
Today I will take you all

42:00.560 --> 42:02.080
to hell with me.

42:36.090 --> 42:37.690
As a noble of the Nine Cities,

42:39.080 --> 42:42.010
you should have worked
for the welfare of the people.

42:42.600 --> 42:45.530
Yet you end up like this
for your own selfish desires.

42:52.080 --> 42:52.850
Everyone.
